<p>I don&#8217;t think they hate America. I just think they love money more. It occurs to me that discussions of America&#8217;s foreign policy failures probably sell pretty well in Europe and Asia. Probably not so well at home&#8211; or perhaps it is believed they will not sell so well at home.</p>
<p>Retreat into isolationism, anyone?</p>
