					<dd class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
						<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-374083">
<p>It isn&#8217;t so much dumbing down as it is hating to be wrong and being reminded of it at every turn.  And on the European and Asian fronts, it is &#8220;Schadenfreude&#8221; &#8211; a German word meaning &#8216;pleasure taken from someone else&#8217;s misfortune&#8217;.</p>
